title: Ep. 429: Leaked Internal Twitter Messages | Gay Superman is 'more heroic'

description: In this episode of For Canon Sake, we talked about leaks obtained by LibsOfTikTok. We also discuss if Duke Nukem could even be made in today's day and age.
